---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import heroBg from "../assets/img/hero-bg.png";
---

<section id="inicio" class="relative w-full min-h-[90vh] flex items-center bg-[#1D1A1A] overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-black">
    <Image src={heroBg} alt="Gimnasio Lima Fit Method" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40" fetchpriority="high" loading="eager" />
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 pt-20 flex justify-center items-center min-h-[80vh]">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <span class="inline-block bg-[#EFD915] text-[#1D1A1A] font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-xs md:text-sm px-4 py-1.5 mt-12 mb-2 rounded-sm">Cobertura en Lima Metropolitana</span>

      <h1 class="italic text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-white leading-[1.1] mb-6 uppercase" style="font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;">
        Transforma tu físico
        <span class="text-[#EFD915]">sin dietas</span> extremas
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-300 mb-5 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Entrenamiento de alto rendimiento con el Lima Fit Method. Resultados sostenibles basados en ciencia, no en restricciones absurdas.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 mb-10">
        <a
          href="#planes"
          class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-10 py-4 text-base font-bold text-[#1D1A1A] bg-[#EFD915] hover:bg-yellow-400 transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest rounded-sm"
        >
          Ver Planes
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
